combinatorics: ʻO ke aʻo ʻana i ka helu, hoʻonohonoho, a hui pū
ka ho\u02bbololi \u02bbana: ʻO ka hoʻonohonoho ʻana o nā mea ma kahi ʻano kikoʻī
hui \u02bbana: ʻO ka pūʻulu o nā mea ʻokoʻa a pau i nā pūʻulu i hāʻawi ʻia
factorial: Huahana o ka huinahelu a me na huina helu a pau malalo iho
helu helu binomial: Ka helu o nā ala e koho ai i kahi ʻāpana o kahi pūʻulu
kumuk\u0101n\u0101wai \u02bb\u014dpua: Inā hoʻokomo ʻia nā mea 'n' i loko o nā pahu 'm' a me n > m, a laila pono e loaʻa i ka pahu hoʻokahi a ʻoi aku ma mua o hoʻokahi mea.
kumu ho\u02bboku\u02bbu ho\u02bbokomo: No nā pūʻulu pau ʻelua, ʻo ka nui o ko lāua hui ʻana ka huina o ko lāua nui me ka nui o ko lāua hui ʻana.
huahana cartesian: ʻO ka huahana o nā pūʻulu he nui, e loaʻa ana i ka pūʻulu o nā hui like ʻole
mana ho\u02bbonohonoho: Hoʻonohonoho o nā ʻāpana ʻāpana āpau o kahi pūʻulu
ho\u02bboka\u02bbawale: He mahele o kahi hoʻonohonoho i nā ʻāpana ʻāwili ʻole
helu bele: Ka helu o nā ala e hoʻokaʻawale i kahi set
helu stirling: Ka helu o nā ala e hoʻokaʻawale i kahi pūʻulu i loko o nā ʻāpana ʻokoʻa ʻole
helu catalan: Ka helu o kekahi mau ʻano ala lattice, hoʻololi, lāʻau binary, etc
ho\u02bbonoho: He hōʻiliʻili o nā mea ʻokoʻa, i manaʻo ʻia he mea i kona pono ponoʻī
\u02bb\u0101pana \u02bb\u0101pana: He pūʻulu i loaʻa nā mea wale nō i loaʻa i kekahi pūʻulu ʻē aʻe
huikau: ʻO ka pūʻulu o nā mea āpau i loko o nā pūʻulu i hāʻawi ʻia
\u02bboko\u02bba: ʻO ka pūʻulu o nā mea a pau i loko o kahi pūʻulu ʻaʻole i kahi pūʻulu ʻē aʻe
ho\u02bbok\u014d: ʻO ka pūʻulu o nā mea a pau ʻaʻole i loko o kahi pūʻulu i hāʻawi ʻia
